<span id="freeTextContainer13009318663154044855">Another read from my long ago when I wanted a bit of glitz &amp; escapism in my life. This fitted the bill perfectly - talk about how the other half lives! If you&apos;re going to have to solve a murder, cruising the Med on a luxury private yacht is certainly the way to do it! <br/><br/>Our &quot;heroine&quot; Daisy has to find a killer &amp; has half-a-dozen suspects to choose from. Okay, the characters are quite stereotyped, there&apos;s the bitter ex-wife, the beautiful young mistress, &amp; of course there&apos;s the rugged, mysterious &amp;</span>
  <span id="freeText13009318663154044855" style="display:none">Another read from my long ago when I wanted a bit of glitz &amp; escapism in my life. This fitted the bill perfectly - talk about how the other half lives! If you're going to have to solve a murder, cruising the Med on a luxury private yacht is certainly the way to do it! <br /><br />Our "heroine" Daisy has to find a killer &amp; has half-a-dozen suspects to choose from. Okay, the characters are quite stereotyped, there's the bitter ex-wife, the beautiful young mistress, &amp; of course there's the rugged, mysterious &amp; of course handsome American PI who, &amp; I don't think I'm giving away any surprises here, Daisy falls for, who'dve thought it eh? ;o)<br /><br /> All-in-all an entertaining fun read to enjoy &amp; not take seriously.</span>
