<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11807625901220401874">Born in Yorkshire, North England, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/203833.Elizabeth_Adler' title='Elizabeth Adler' rel='nofollow noopener'>Elizabeth Adler</a> met her husband Richard (an American) while both were working in London. They have lived in England, Ireland, France, Brazil, and the United States and have traveled extensively. They have one daughter and live in Palm Springs, California. Her first novel, Private Desires (also titled Leonie), launched an enormously successful writing career, she a</span>
  <span id="freeText11807625901220401874" style="display:none">Born in Yorkshire, North England, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/203833.Elizabeth_Adler" title="Elizabeth Adler" rel="nofollow noopener">Elizabeth Adler</a> met her husband Richard (an American) while both were working in London. They have lived in England, Ireland, France, Brazil, and the United States and have traveled extensively. They have one daughter and live in Palm Springs, California. Her first novel, Private Desires (also titled Leonie), launched an enormously successful writing career, she also wrote as <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/403574.Ariana_Scott" title="Ariana Scott" rel="nofollow noopener">Ariana Scott</a>. She has now written over twenty internationally acclaimed bestsellers.</span>
